message: Strategy: Always cook raw protein and vegetables with the stove first; they become 20 value. For grains, cook them with the stove (they usually stay 0 value), then combine the cooked grain with water to get a 20-value 'soaked cooked grain'. Combine one cooked protein and one cooked vegetable for a 60-value item. Then, add a 'soaked cooked grain' to this combination to reach 80-100 value. Be careful not to add a fourth item to a high-value dish, as this can drop the value to 0. Submit once you hit 100.
